Package: piccr
Title: Correct and Calibrate Picarro CRDS Stable Isotope Data
Version: 1.1.0.9000
Author: Thomas Muench [aut, cre],
    Tom Wollnik [aut]
Maintainer: Thomas Muench <thomas.muench@awi.de>
Description: This R package provides tools to process raw stable isotopologue
    data of water measured by Picarro Inc. cavity ring-down spectroscopy
    measurement devices including memory correction, drift correction,
    calibration and assessment of quality control information.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests:
    bookdown,
    covr,
    devtools,
    knitr,
    rlist,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:
    dplyr,
    lubridate,
    purrr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr,
    yaml
URL: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/piccr
BugReports: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/piccr/issues
